Additional Products – True Drinks




 























 





















        

















True Drinks development team is actively pursuing additional beverage products that will complement our current lineup.  There has been a trend in the marketplace towards drinks that are low in calories, free of artificial ingredients, and supportive of a healthy diet and lifestyle.
The soda industry is on the ropes as study after study lays childhood obesity, juvenile diabetes, early onset heart disease and more at their feet.
We are pursuing line extensions into schools (primary and secondary) as vitamin-infused, sugar-free alternatives.
As well as a new option for Mom and Dads, vitamin enhanced water available in natural flavors that parents appreciate.










