Company Summary
True Drinks Holdings, Inc is a manufacturer and marketer of beverages and health snack products. Its brand portfolio consists of AquaBall, a naturally flavoured water drink primarily for kids and teens. True Drinks Holdings Inc., formerly known as Bazi International, is based in Irvine, California.   

















 


















